Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:33.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all the world is stereotypical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're Playing out rules
