Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now you thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you had me by the upper － hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but I see through the face you've covered cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:41.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( FOUR )
