Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Without the fear and tears surrounding you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:48.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:55.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ今まで生きるstrategy 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:56.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:22:58.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハンドルを切って暴れ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢のまま突き進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:06.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍のない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:08.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:11.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:16.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:23.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ask yourself, the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:26.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去も傷も恐れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来さえも捨てるようなもんだ
