Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:33.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is what I choose to live for
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== MAIN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您總算醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大概十七年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我睡的時間還真長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬 一切都還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你已經甦醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就終於能開演第二幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 是時候對巫師氣息落下正義的鐵錘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,請下您的第一個命令 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們隨時都能夠戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他們現在還存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要做什麼就不用我說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,各位都明白自己該做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,6月15日 上午7點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,隨著自上次大戰一直沉睡著的亡者引路人當家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,龍泉寺和馬的甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次魔法大戰拉開了帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那暗示著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,到底將要發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下節課要換教室了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.41,NOTE,,0,0,0,,這麼突然 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,武 你看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,紅色的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,果然和夢中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,伊田 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是去雙葉那了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 伊田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的雙葉…把我的雙葉還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雙…葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點 六
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,武和胡桃也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你…果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,防護
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不准對我的妹妹動手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 六
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,午安 四條院長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,赤龍的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看來她不記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看了我們的魔法會想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,建議你覺悟好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是為了消滅你才組成的隊伍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可別一個人先衝哦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾 看來赤龍和引路人是聯手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得你們是在崩壞世界的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所向披靡的三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是操縱氣壓的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而你旁邊的是封閉空間的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你知道也防不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFGMinchoP_U-W5\fs63}在深夜的鶇哪裡也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,旋動鎖錠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,膠囊牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗之門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的魔力最大限度也只是一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們三人的魔力全聚集到一個人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這個結界你是打不破的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個空間由我們支配著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起不可視之神的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在空白之中 窒息而亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,房間裡應該是無法呼吸的真空才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑之窗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,結界被…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,應該由我們所支配著的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是搭了個便車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道站在中間的你通過抓著兩邊人的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,展開了避免處於真空環境的防禦結界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我也就加進了你們這個電車遊戲之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是毫無目的地發動了黑暗之門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,發動的同時在他背後製造了個微小的洞口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,答案對完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,該是結束的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,5M·武器庫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要是在學校時有好好學習暗黑魔法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或許還能夠對應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,實在漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是四條學院長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你被開除了 維歐莉特老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然殺了我可愛的學生們 真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,別在那裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是一直在一旁看著嗎 真虧你能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在結果了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這結局真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫忙看下伊田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們剛才發現他倒在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是到現在還沒恢復意識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伊田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 六
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,交給老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只是昏過去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要躺著休息一下 過一會自然就醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才聽說古代赤龍的學生在襲擊學院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是學院之中好像也混入了引路人的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,武 五十島 我來接你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別過去 五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 你為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說是來接你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,直覺迴避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,迴避魔法能預知未來的危險從而躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真有武的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這是膽小鬼才學的魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,武 其實你已經感覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我的弟弟會突然改變態度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,心中在想 難道是原諒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,之類的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島 你退後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,月光是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,引路人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對 我是引路人的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是因為最初教我魔法的是引路人的成員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,武和五十島也見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,叫鷲津吉平的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 快退出引路人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃 那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因為在引路人這邊能讓武嚐嚐苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,讓想要殺掉我的武嚐嚐苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 武只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,月光快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,天使之手能瞬間移動到各種場所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想試試和武的直覺迴避比哪個更快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心就刺下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你發覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我都還沒解除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島 快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為胡桃能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下吧 為什麼我會得到這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對於腿腳不好的我 這能力剛好合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛是神在和我說 去把武痛打一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,從這傢伙毀了我的時候開始 這命運就已經定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來 武
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,離這遠點 五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只能這樣解決是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 殺了我你就能滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊 誰說過要殺你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,先是因為 那個 維歐莉特盯上你的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那會到我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,還有就是想讓胡桃加入引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 武就是想佔有全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,武 別再說這說那了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你那樣真的很煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如永夜中降下的落雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,飛翔至冥府盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,吾之名為墮落者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,飛馳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,武 武
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃 離開他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,武…武…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃 快離開他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,武…武…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃是屬於我的 薄暮也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,七瀨 武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,武 快醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在做夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,武 我能所做的只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還有月光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,月光把媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,武 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來接我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆 永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰 你在對武做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好 我是小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下週主要講卡美洛大祭司日本支部的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,順便說一下卡美洛大祭司是只由女性構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止男性加入的聯盟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說會聯想到女性之間的禁斷之戀什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,順便一說我也有過以為對方是男性
